title: 'The Girl in the Spider's Web' by David Lagercrantz tops Maclean's fiction list
text:
The Canadian Press - ONLINE EDITION 'The Girl in the Spider's Web' by David Lagercrantz tops Maclean's fiction list By: The Canadian Press 
Here are the top 10 hardcover fiction and non-fiction books in Canada for the week ending Oct. 11 as compiled by Maclean's magazine. The previous week's position is in parentheses. 
FICTION 
1. (1) The Girl in the Spider's Web _ David Lagercrantz 
2. (3) The Heart Goes Last _ Margaret Atwood 
3. (6) Go Set a Watchman _ Harper Lee 
4. (4) Make Me (A Jack Reacher Novel) _ Lee Child 
5. (10) The Illegal _ Lawrence Hill 
6. (-) The Murder House _ James Patterson and David Ellis
